{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_零工接活",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·零工接活（拉具路倒，糊口腌臜活）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "flow_背尸_淹尸活",
              "state": "accepted"
            }
          ],
          "next": "yan_remind"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "flow_背尸_淹尸活",
              "state": "carrying"
            }
          ],
          "next": "yan_carrying"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "flow_背尸_淹尸活",
              "state": "delivered",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "yan_done"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "零工背尸_done",
              "op": "==",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "yan_offer"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一个挑着空担的汉子看到关二狗，努了努嘴。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "巷子尾头躺了具死人子，没得人认。拉切义庄，给你五文。整不整？",
      "next": "n_choice",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「五文就五文。死人钱好挣得很。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        },
        {
          "id": "xian",
          "text": "「才五文索？……算了，拉就拉。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_jie": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗啐了口唾沫搓搓手——上前，过肩，搭手。背死人子的老把式，闭着眼睛都不会错。",
      "next": "n_carry"
    },
    "n_carry": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "carry_ordinary_corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_more"
    },
    "n_more": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（努嘴往巷子深处）那点还撂起一具，吊死的老汉。一路拉了，再给你五文。",
      "next": "n_carry2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n_carry2": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "carry_ordinary_corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_done"
    },
    "n_done": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "零工背尸_done",
            "value": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "yan_offer": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "又是你嗦。正好——河头今早捞起个泡涨的，官面验过，没得人认。拉切义庄，八文。整不整？",
      "next": "yan_choice"
    },
    "yan_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「八文就八文。淹的又咋个，一样背。」",
          "next": "yan_ok"
        },
        {
          "id": "buji",
          "text": "「泡涨的死人子沉得很……等老子缓口气。」",
          "next": "yan_no"
        }
      ]
    },
    "yan_ok": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_零工接活",
            "signal": "beishi_yan_accepted"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "yan_ok_line"
    },
    "yan_ok_line": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "死人子在码头巷口，苇席底下撂起。莫拖——日头毒了要出味。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "yan_no": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "要得，想通了再来。死人子又跑不脱。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "yan_remind": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "还没去嗦？码头巷口，苇席底下。手脚麻利点。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "yan_carrying": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "背都背起了还杵到这做啥子？义庄，快切！",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "yan_done": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "淹的那个交了嗦？要得。回头再有活路喊你。",
      "next": "end1"
    }
  }
}
